            {
               "text": "<center><div class=\"first_steps_reflection_parent\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection question_mark\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-brain\"></i></div><div class=\"first_steps_reflection\"><b>Reflection 2: I, you, he/she...</b><br /><br />Observe the structure at Copán, Honduras.<br /><br />Where would you place the numbers we use for counting (0, 1, 2...)?<br /><br />Where would you place the other numbers (1, ..., 1.2, ..., 1.3, ..., 2, ..., 2.4)?</div></div></center>",
